---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="headshot slide-in-block">
    <Image
      src="/img/headshot.jpeg"
      alt="Tyler Crosse"
      width={300}
      height={300}
    />
  </div>

  <section class="intro slide-in-block">
    <h1>Hi, I'm Tyler üëã</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      I'm a software engineer turned graduate student, currently pursuing my
      passion for understanding how computers work ‚Äî from the silicon to
      systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="journey slide-in-block">
    <h2>My Journey</h2>
    <p>
      My path to computer science has been anything but conventional. I started
      with a degree in <strong>Biomedical Engineering</strong> from VCU, thinking
      I'd build medical devices. Instead, I found myself drawn to the software side‚Äîbuilding
      web applications, distributed systems, and eventually leading engineering teams.
    </p>
    <p>
      After nearly a decade in industry, <a
        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AlphaFold"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">AlphaFold's breakthrough in 2018</a
      >
      crystallized something for me: machine learning wasn't just another tool‚Äîit
      was going to revolutionize science in ways I hadn't imagined. That realization
      sent me back to school to build the foundational knowledge I needed to be part
      of that revolution.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="experience slide-in-block">
    <h2>Experience</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item current">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Georgia Institute of Technology</h3>
          <p class="company">
            MS Computer Science <span class="period">| 2024 - Present</span>
          </p>

          <p class="description">
            Specializing in Machine Learning and High-Performance Computing.
            Deep diving into operating systems, distributed systems, and the
            mathematical foundations of ML. Building everything from
            multithreaded servers in C to neural networks from scratch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Knowable</h3>
          <p class="company">
            Lead Software Engineer <span class="period">| 5 years</span>
          </p>

          <p class="description">
            Led engineering initiatives on an audio learning platform. Built
            scalable backend systems, mentored junior developers, and
            architected solutions for millions of users. Worked across the full
            stack from React frontends to distributed microservices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Rosetta Stone</h3>
          <p class="company">
            Senior Software Engineer <span class="period">| 2 years</span>
          </p>

          <p class="description">
            Contributed to the language learning platform that's helped millions
            of people learn new languages. Focused on backend systems and API
            development, working with international teams across multiple time
            zones.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <h3>Virginia Commonwealth University</h3>
          <p class="company">BS Biomedical Engineering</p>

          <p class="description">
            Where it all started. Studied the intersection of engineering and
            medicine, but discovered my true passion lay in the computational
            side of solving complex problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="interests slide-in-block">
    <h2>What I'm Into</h2>
    <div class="interests-grid">
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>üß† Machine Learning</h3>
        <p>
          From neural networks to optimization algorithms, I'm fascinated by how
          we can teach machines to learn patterns and make decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>‚ö° High-Performance Computing</h3>
        <p>
          There's something beautiful about squeezing every ounce of performance
          out of hardware‚Äîparallel processing, GPU computing, distributed
          systems.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>üîß Systems Programming</h3>
        <p>
          Getting close to the metal. Understanding how operating systems work,
          how memory is managed, how processes communicate.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>üìö Learning in Public</h3>
        <p>
          Sharing the journey, the failures, and the breakthroughs. Building
          knowledge in the open where others can learn alongside me.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>üß¨ Computational Biology</h3>
        <p>
          Understanding the biological processes that underlie disease and
          development.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="interest-card">
        <h3>‚öñÔ∏è Economics</h3>
        <p>Understanding the economic forces that shape our world.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-this-site slide-in-block">
    <h2>About This Digital Garden</h2>
    <p>
      This site is my <strong>digital garden</strong>‚Äîa place where ideas can
      grow and evolve over time. Unlike a traditional blog, content here isn't
      organized chronologically but by connections and themes. Some pieces are
      polished articles, others are rough notes or works in progress.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe in <strong>learning in public</strong>, sharing not just the
      final results but the messy process of figuring things out. If you see
      something interesting, wrong, or want to discuss an idea,
      <a href="mailto:hello@tylercrosse.com">drop me a line</a>!
    </p>

    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a>. Check out the <a href="https://github.com/tylercrosse/personal-site" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">source code</a>. It would be a little weird to just copy it wholesale.
    </p>

    <details class="inspiration-details">
      <summary>Sites that inspired this one</summary>
      <ul class="inspiration-list">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://distill.pub/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Distill.pub</strong>
          </a> - Interactive machine learning research papers
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://maggieappleton.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Maggie Appleton</strong>
          </a> - The digital garden philosophy and beautiful visual thinking
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.arlenmccluskey.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Arlen McCluskey</strong>
          </a> - Clean technical writing and site structure
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://eugeneyan.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Eugene Yan</strong>
          </a> - Thoughtful ML content and career insights
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.swyx.io/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Swyx</strong>
          </a> - Learning in public and developer advocacy
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://lowyx.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <strong>Yxlow</strong>
          </a> - Minimalist design and thoughtful curation
        </li>
      </ul>
    </details>
  </section>

  <style>
    section {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .headshot {
      margin: 2rem auto;
      max-width: 300px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .headshot img {
      border: 8px solid #fff;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .intro h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--sol-base01);
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--sol-base0);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .journey {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .journey p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      /* margin: 2rem 0; */
    }
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      /* padding-left: 60px; */
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      position: absolute;
      left: 11px;
      top: 8px;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--sol-base2);
      border: 3px solid var(--sol-base3);
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
      color: var(--sol-base01);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .company {
      color: var(--sol-blue);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    }

    .description {
      color: var(--sol-base0);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .interests-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .interest-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: var(--sol-base01);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .interest-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--sol-base0);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* .about-this-site {
        background: var(--sol-base3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--sol-base2);
      } */

    .about-this-site p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .inspiration-details {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .inspiration-details summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--sol-base01);
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sol-base2);
    }

    .inspiration-details summary:hover {
      color: var(--sol-blue);
    }
    .inspiration-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .inspiration-list a {
      color: var(--sol-blue);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .inspiration-list a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .slide-in-block {
      opacity: 0;
      filter: blur(10px);
      transform: scale(0.95);
      will-change: transform, opacity, filter;
      animation: slideInBlock 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.43, 0.195, 0.02, 1) forwards;
    }

    .slide-in-block:nth-child(1) {
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }
    .slide-in-block:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: 0.1s;
    }
    .slide-in-block:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }
    .slide-in-block:nth-child(4) {
      animation-delay: 0.3s;
    }
    .slide-in-block:nth-child(5) {
      animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }
    .slide-in-block:nth-child(6) {
      animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }

    @keyframes slideInBlock {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        filter: blur(0px);
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }

    /* Dark theme adjustments */
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .headshot img {
        /* border-color: var(--sol-base02); */
      }

      .interest-card {
        background: var(--sol-base02);
        border-color: var(--sol-base01);
      }

      .about-this-site {
        background: var(--sol-base02);
        border-color: var(--sol-base01);
      }

      .timeline::before {
        background: var(--sol-base01);
      }

      .timeline-marker {
        background: var(--sol-base01);
        border-color: var(--sol-base02);
      }
    }

    /* Mobile responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .intro h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .lead {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .interests-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .timeline-item {
        padding-left: 50px;
      }

      .timeline::before {
        left: 15px;
      }

      .timeline-marker {
        left: 6px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
